Package cna.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alignment
    Represents an alignment in sam/bam format.
    Annotation
    Represents gene and repeat annotation for a distinct genomic region
    DataBase
    Provides basic functionality for database communication
    DataSet
    Represents a data set of genomic alignments in sam/bam format.
    Gene
    Represents a gene annotation
    Genome
    Represents a genome build.
    Individual
    Represents a distinct individual in the data base (patient or animal).
    Label
    Represents a classification label (i.e. healthy or disease)
    ReadPair
    Represends a paired-end sequencing read pair
    Region
    Represents a distinct region on the genome.
    Repeat
    Represents a genomic repeat region.
    RepeatMasker
    Provides functionality to obtain repeat masks from an annotation database
